# Portfolio Analytics Workflow - Instruction Map

This instruction map shows how to compose core_engine components into a comprehensive portfolio analytics system for institutional-grade performance measurement, attribution analysis, and risk assessment.

## Portfolio Analytics Component Stack

### Analytics Brick Assembly
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
│    HierarchicalSystemOrchestrator   │ ← System Control & Coordination
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│ PortfolioDataManager                │ ← Portfolio & Benchmark Data
│ TransactionDataManager              │ ← Trade & Execution Data
│ MarketDataManager                   │ ← Market & Reference Data
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│ PerformanceCalculator               │ ← Returns & Risk Metrics
│ AttributionAnalyzer                 │ ← Performance Attribution
│ RiskAnalyzer                        │ ← Risk Decomposition
│ BenchmarkAnalyzer                   │ ← Benchmark Comparison
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│ FactorAnalyzer                      │ ← Factor Exposure Analysis
│ StyleAnalyzer                       │ ← Style & Sector Analysis
│ RegimeAnalyzer                      │ ← Regime-Based Analytics
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│ ReportGenerator                     │ ← Comprehensive Reporting
│ VisualizationEngine                 │ ← Advanced Charting
│ AlertSystem                         │ ← Performance Alerts
└─────────────────────────────────────┘
```

